The steps for C# in Visual Code:

dotnet new console

(dotnet restore //this is optional, if .NET is >= 2)

dotnet build
or
dotnet run





https://www.microsoft.com/net/learn/get-started/macos
(The above is for visual studio code, on the other hand, we could also use the visual studio for any .net application)

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/core/tutorials/with-visual-studio-code







